Text: REPST Darron Call me when you get a chance I have tried getting to you a couple times with no success Jay Original Message From mailto Sent Monday January PM To Subject RE The HB was pretty wild We went to the Big XII CG Good game bummer outcome I think I would like to start the plan for each kid Can I transfer either the custodial or Ed IRA I just tried to call but no one answered With all the craziness here Im not sitting by my phone If you call ask the person to messenger me DG Original Message From liberman Jay H DALLAS EY ENRON Sent Thursday January PM To Giron Darron C Subject RE Darron Sorry things have been hectic lately How did you like that Horns game As for the Ed IRA they have raised the limits to K You should however consider the Section plans that I believe we have discussed previously Call me to discuss further Jay Original Message From Giron Darron C mailtoDarronC NRONcom Sent Thursday January PM To Jay Liberman Email Subject FW Original Message From Giron Darron C Sent Friday January AM To Jay Liberman Email Subject Jay I hope you had a good Holiday Season Hopefully will be better than I believe that this year the limit has been raised on the Education
